Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.21,0:00:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要吃我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,多宝丸之卷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,已经两个月没下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,再这样下去  收成就会受影响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下  邻国的朝仓有些动静
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,调查到与敌国接壤的边境城市里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有兵力正在秘密调集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在他们起兵之前  我们应该先下手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那不寻常的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,果然那才是父亲隐瞒的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,陆奥 兵库
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,想请你们做点事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:03:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让家里人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是那个婴儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他想要取回被你们夺走的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,然后  听那个商人大叔说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那个国家很富饶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的世道也能让大家饱饱的吃上饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样  很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,下个目标就去那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大赚一笔  然后饱餐一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,鲷鱼火锅  干鲍鱼  包子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,包子?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,软软的  甜甜的  非常好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,啊说起来之前就想问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那个护身符的图案  是家纹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是大哥哥家的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,已经喂他了药
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不论什么他都会如实回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲给你下达了特殊命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,命令了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,去找十六年前失踪的婴儿和接生婆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,婴儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲为什么要找那个婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他想把舌头咬断
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不  伤口不是很深
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,受药物的影响使不出力气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲  你在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,朝仓局面紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这个?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲  为什么要找那个婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还是十几年前出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲大人拜祭的无头佛像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是和那个有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,请回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不说第二遍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你们能找到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,小的时候一有事就会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每次都这样接您回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,每一次都是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在父亲眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在依然是个小孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以打仗也不让我出战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密也不跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次见到父亲那样的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,婴儿那件事就这么重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,求您发发慈悲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,别扔下我们不管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不放手的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,多宝丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在回宅邸的路上经过这村子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人就突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请帮帮我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去全村人都会被妖怪吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,旋涡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始以为只是小波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,突然就变成旋涡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,正要被旋涡卷进去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有一张像人一样的嘴在等着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它把整船的人都吞下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,已经有许多村民牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,旋涡和人的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,的确像是魑魅魍魉之类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我去帮你们消灭那个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,多宝丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,您是打算相信这些村人的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,即使他们说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但消灭妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人没有说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,人民在受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我坐视不理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果怕妖怪你们就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,多宝丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你们害怕的话也别跟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,您在开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,少主去的话哪怕是地狱我也奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那个… 船桨动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,拉绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是不动的话就吃不到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,螃蟹妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,竟如此狰狞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看我马上斩了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,王八蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然从水里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,多宝丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,拉绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,上岸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,它伤得也不轻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,所以应该追不上来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如果再捅几次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,船就撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,果然战场那一套在这里不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办少主？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我多言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙靠嘴捕食猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,事先将火药藏到怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,只要让它吃到嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就马上引爆它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然它外壳很硬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但里面应该很脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一定可以杀死妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,和被吃掉的人一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,和妖怪同归于尽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,都说会死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们兄弟是为了保护少主而活的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们死了就没法保护您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,眼前这片景色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,山中绿意盎然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,泉下溪水满溢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,稻田满是稻米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是醍醐的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是听说在我出生之前不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,由于水灾种不了庄稼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,百姓嚼着树根
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,煎熬度日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而让它变得如此富饶的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的父亲 醍醐景光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而我是他的儿子 多宝丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一只小小妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我定会除掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要做的不是去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,而是相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,兵库 把我举起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,再高 再高一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,陆奥 把大家召集起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只有这一招对付它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你们愿意做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,出现了吗 妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,打开水闸!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,在湖的附近 散布着很多小湖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,通过水闸连接着其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果把水从另一个水闸放走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,便会如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,终于现身了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这次定会除掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你们后退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来 陆奥 兵库
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然这么简单就把那恐怖的妖怪给…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,多宝丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,请替我们报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,多宝丸大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 可恶的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,快去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看来到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就让你解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,保护水闸!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,兵库!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
